title: The MOST Overlooked Team In 2021 Is...
description:
Linda and Emily look back on the 2021 season and highlight a few players before looking ahead to what they hope to see heading into the new year with new COVID protocols. Linda also mentions who she believes is the most overlooked team in 2021... and you'd be surprised who it is!
